ttcut (0.50.0-1~forky) forky; urgency=medium

  * Major release: H.264/H.265 Smart Cut support
  * Frame-accurate cutting for elementary streams (.264, .265)
  * Re-encode only at cut points (~0.5% of frames)
  * Stream-copy for remaining frames (lossless, ~99.5%)
  * Multi-segment support with audio cutting
  * MKV muxing via mkvmerge
  * Native NAL unit parser with memory-mapped I/O

 -- MINIXJR <35893755+MINIXJR@users.noreply.github.com>  Fri, 30 Jan 2026 20:07:21 +0100

